  No. 4000140320/23/I-NS, Destination Earth Use Cases 2023). Finally,
  M.W. and T.O. acknowledge support from the Digital Twin of the Ocean –
  Animal Tracking (DTO Track) project funded by the Sustainable Blue
  Economy Partnership (ANR-24-SBEP-0001).</p>
</sec>
</body>
